    <item>
      <title>美国联邦贸易委员会提起的亚马逊反垄断诉讼在裁决后将取得进展</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-07/amazon-antitrust-case-filed-by-ftc-to-move-forward-after-ruling</link>
      <description><![CDATA[亚马逊公司必须面对美国联邦贸易委员会就其在线市场提起的反垄断诉讼，但联邦法官驳回了该机构与州消费者保护法相关的一些指控。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-07/amazon-antitrust-case-filed-by-ftc-to-move-forward-after-ruling</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 07 Oct 2024 17:25:25 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>肯尼亚副总统将在议会抗辩弹劾</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-07/kenya-s-deputy-president-to-fight-impeachment-in-parliament</link>
      <description><![CDATA[肯尼亚副总统里加蒂·加查瓜 (Rigathi Gachagua) 表示，他将于周二出席国民议会，为自己在弹劾程序中违反宪法的指控进行辩护。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-07/kenya-s-deputy-president-to-fight-impeachment-in-parliament</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 07 Oct 2024 16:46:31 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>芝加哥市长在最新动荡中任命新学校董事会</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-07/chicago-mayor-appoints-a-new-school-board-in-latest-upheaval</link>
      <description><![CDATA[芝加哥市长布兰登·约翰逊周一宣布了该市公立学校董事会的新成员名单。此前，约翰逊上周表示，由于预算短缺问题日益紧张，他之前任命的所有董事会成员都将辞职。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-07/chicago-mayor-appoints-a-new-school-board-in-latest-upheaval</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 07 Oct 2024 16:23:35 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>伊丽莎白·沃伦敦促可口可乐、百事可乐、通用磨坊应对缩减通胀</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-07/warren-presses-coca-cola-pepsi-general-mills-on-shrinkflation</link>
      <description><![CDATA[可口可乐、百事可乐和通用磨坊正受到参议院民主党人伊丽莎白·沃伦和众议员玛德琳·迪恩的审查，她们指责这些公司利用紧缩性通胀来牟取消费者的暴利。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-07/warren-presses-coca-cola-pepsi-general-mills-on-shrinkflation</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 07 Oct 2024 16:21:42 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>美国就 F-35 达成的协议让洛克希德公司得以收回被扣留的款项</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-07/us-deal-on-f-35s-allows-lockheed-to-win-back-withheld-payments</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据美国项目经理称，五角大楼已与洛克希德·马丁公司就该公司可在年底前达到的里程碑达成一致，以获得因缺乏必要的硬件和软件升级而可能被扣留的 5 亿美元付款中的一部分。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-07/us-deal-on-f-35s-allows-lockheed-to-win-back-withheld-payments</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 07 Oct 2024 16:00:16 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>美国国家安全局正在调查中国黑客是否入侵美国电信公司</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-07/nsa-investigating-if-chinese-hackers-breached-us-telecom-firms</link>
      <description><![CDATA[一位高级情报官员透露，美国正对中国可能攻击美国电信公司的事件展开初步调查。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-07/nsa-investigating-if-chinese-hackers-breached-us-telecom-firms</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 07 Oct 2024 15:59:46 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>以色列称在战争一周年之际拦截了哈马斯火箭弹</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-07/israel-says-it-intercepted-hamas-rockets-as-war-marks-one-year</link>
      <description><![CDATA[以色列国防军称，他们拦截了伊朗支持的哈马斯向特拉维夫发射的大部分火箭弹，经过一年的战争，双方的战斗于周一进一步升级。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-07/israel-says-it-intercepted-hamas-rockets-as-war-marks-one-year</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 07 Oct 2024 15:56:09 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>纽约市“放射性”市长从狂妄自大变为麻木不仁</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-07/eric-adams-investigation-nyc-s-mayor-goes-from-swagger-to-chaos</link>
      <description><![CDATA[市长面临刑事指控，他的亲密盟友正在逃离政府，警察局的高层陷入混乱。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-07/eric-adams-investigation-nyc-s-mayor-goes-from-swagger-to-chaos</guid>
